snippet.title: Preview of my DK Jungle climber 64 DS Hack!
snippet.description: This is pretty much the latest update so far of what I have. There's a little more to complete though, but I'm mostly done. You can see more details on http://kuribo64.net/board/thread.php?id=3480 and also download the hack there. Any credits are included on Kuribo64.
